title: $:/litClock/times/-17:53-Talbot Baines Reed
quote_first: “That boy will be spoiled, as sure as I go on springs; he’s made such a lot of. Have you been regulated?” “I should think I have!” exclaimed I, in indignant recollection of my education. “All right; keep your temper. What time are you?” “
quoteSourceTitle: The Adventures of a Three-Guinea Watch
